node.text:
I’ve been working on my mental toughness for a while…
.
The reality is that after losing it all and
getting extremely depressed…
.
I gave up on life…
.
For a while, I stopped trying…
.
There was no point to keep trying…
.
All the evidence, the hundreds of thousands of dollars I owed to the banks, and my destructive personality was pointing to 1 thing.
.
That I was only good at 1 thing.
.
I’m good at failing.
.
So, I became a little pussy in my mind and the victim mentality took over.
.
I started getting drunk 4 times a week and then using heavy drugs to scape the deep feelings of failure.
.
Thank God that I started reading books from guys like @davidgoggins @andyfrisella and other MF’s that had it worse than me in many areas.
.
These MF’s inspired me through their speaking and stories of how they became the relentless MF they are today.
.
I’m extremely grateful to these guys. I wouldn’t be where I am today without them.
.
There have been a handful of transformative books that helped me get out of homelessness and become a person that I’m truly proud.
.
I’ll be giving away 3 real life changing books for 3 people that share this post on their stories.
.
See you at the top!
.
Hope you win 🏆!

node.text:
All of the following is 100% true, real life Stuff, most of it, I’m not proud of, but, it shaped me…

I’ve been robbed
I’ve been handcuffed 
I’ve been in jail
I’ve been high
I’ve been overdosed 
I’ve been chased by the cops
I’ve been beaten
I’ve been punched in the face
I’ve run for my life
I’ve hidden for months from my enemies
I’ve been homeless 
I’ve spent 9 days with no food
Partners been in jail for years
My business went on fire and I lost it all
I’ve been sick
I have had 4 surgeries 
I’ve been lost
For a while I seriously thought I was crazy
I’ve been sued
One of my business partners killed his wife and committed suicide 
I’ve been scammed by people I considered family
I’ve been to the psychiatrist 
I’ve done hypnotherapy 
I’ve done weed
I’ve done coke
I’ve done crack
I’ve done ayahuasca 
I’ve done mushrooms 
I’ve done 5-MEO-DMT
I’ve had hallucinations
I’ve been beating 
I’ve been alone for long periods 
I’ve been extremely scared
I’ve been suicidal
I’ve had $60k days
I’ve failed 8 different businesses 
I lost everything 4 times
I’ve slept in trains
I’ve slept in airports
I’ve slept in warehouses 
I’ve slept in my car
I’ve been stupid beyond measure
I’ve been depressed 
I’ve been broken
I’ve been through hell

But, I’m still here, I never gave up by the Grace of God 👁 i even discovered that all of this time I’ve been guided, I’m still alive, I’ve been taking care of.

I’ve understood that all all of that didn’t happened to me, it happened for me, to teach me, to kill the little bitch inside of me, to shape a warrior in me.

All of that happened to chip away everything that’s not THE REAL JOE.

#warrior #therealjoe #tattoo #warriortattoo #lion #liontattoo #eyeofprovidence #wisdom
